snippet.title: Maneater reveal trailer - PC Gaming Show 2018
snippet.description:
Maneater is an open world action-RPG, and you're the shark bent on hunting human and ocean prey alike. Evolve your body to become the ultimate hunter.

See more on http://www.pcgamer.com and watch the PC Gaming Show livestream at https://www.pcgamer.com/pc-gaming-show-2018-watch/
